        </div>
        <h3 class="tc-atlas-h">Face &amp; multi-monitor</h3>
        <p class="tc-atlas-d">Face-presence sampled at 4 Hz; off-frame events &gt; 3 seconds are logged. Multi-screen and external display attachment detected via the Screen Capture API.</p>
        <a class="tc-atlas-link" href="/aquintutor/exams">Read &nbsp;&rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="tc-atlas-card">
        <div class="tc-atlas-icon">
