          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Score report within 5 days</li>
